<h1><b>Bill Finger</h1>
<h2>The Co-Creator of the Caped Crusader</b></h2>
<p><img src="https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/en/0/09/Bill_finger_photo.jpg">
</p>

<p>Bill Finger is the co-creator of the DC Comics super hero character: Batman. DC Comics artist Bob Kane created the original design for Batman, and Bill Finger was brought on to help write the story. Bill was uncredited for decades for his contributions, with DC Comics leading the public to believe Bob Kane was the sole creator of Batman. Bill’s legacy came to light thanks in part to Mark Tyler Noble’s book <a href='https://www.amazon.com/Bill-Boy-Wonder-Secret-Co-Creator/dp/1580892892' target=blank>Bill the Boy Wonder: The Secret Co-Creator of Batman</a>.</p>

